WEBVTT

22:51.070 --> 22:51.760 line:80%
What?

22:52.630 --> 22:53.630 line:80%
A few days ago,

22:53.830 --> 22:55.040 line:80%
I thought for a long time

22:55.040 --> 22:57.040 line:80%
and finally came up with a solution.

22:58.390 --> 22:59.480 line:80%
I came to tell you

23:00.260 --> 23:02.720 line:80%
that I'm willing to take you
as my concubine.
